TDL Week 8: SWLA high school football scores - KPLC 7 News, Lake Charles, Louisiana Member Center: TDL Week 8: SWLA high school football scores Posted: (Source: KPLC) SOUTHWEST LOUISIANA (KPLC) - 
Keep checking with us all night for all the high school football scores from around Southwest Louisiana. Mobile users, click HERE for scores. 
After the games, Brady Renard and Mike Gaither will have all the highlights on your TV, on your desktop or on your smartphone . Remember, Touchdown Live begins at 10:15 p.m.. 
Send your Friday night football photos to newmedia@kplctv.com and we'll add them to our weekly slideshow. 
Thursday Scores South Beauregard 27, Westlake 24 East Beauregard 32, Oberlin 8 Hamilton Christian 61, Lake Charles College Prep 0 SWLA Home School 38, Berchman Academy 0
